" RltvNmbr.vim
"   Author: Charles E. Campbell
"   Date:   Dec 14, 2016
"   Version: 4b	ASTRO-ONLY
"   GetLatestVimScripts: 2351 1 :AutoInstall: RltvNmbr.vim
